{
  "stem": "9728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, there were probably about 30, 40 dead a day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Officially, legally, the grave was supposed to be 120 centimeters, which is, which is, I would say, probably around-- when I dug later I dug the graves, they were supposed to go above our head.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "However, it did not work out this way always, because sometimes, you know, the graves were not ready.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were  dead people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we had to bury them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was one, one body, one body to a grave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The bodies were treated fairly  nice-- well, not nice.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fairly Decent.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not-- some of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was-- the funny part about it was there was a cantor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Jewish bodies were put to grave by a Jewish man, who went down to the grave and put them down-- to the same people that they were grave diggers before the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They, they still performed the ceremonies of the thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if someone could afford-- if someone was in the bureaucracy-- if someone was in the bureaucracy the cantor even said the [HEBREW] and Kaddish.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And those people-- some of them were dead that they didn't have anyone.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We just carried them out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they just put them into the grave and, and buried them there.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
